{"_id":"KdeOSTp53afRtLLT","name":"Gentleman","type":"class","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>As a gentleman, you gain the following class features.</div>\n<h3> </h3>\n<h3>Hit Points</h3>\n<div><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per gentleman level</div>\n<div><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level: </strong>10 + your Constitution modifier</div>\n<div><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per gentleman level after 1st</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Proficiencies</h3>\n<div><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor, shields</div>\n<div><strong>Weapons: </strong>Martial weapons</div>\n<div><strong>Tools: </strong>Dice set</div>\n<div><strong>Saving Throws: </strong>Wisdom, Charisma</div>\n<div><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two skills from Arcana, Deception, Investigation, Performance, Persuasion, Religion, Sleight of Hand</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Equipment</h3>\n<div>You start with the following equipment, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</div>\n<ul>\n<li>(a) studded leather armor (b) leather armor, longbow, and 20 arrows</li>\n<li>(a) a martial weapon and a shield or (b) two martial weapons</li>\n<li>(a) a dungeoneer’s pack or (b) an explorer’s pack</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Gentleman Advancement</h1>\n<div>\n<table style=\"width:100%\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"text-align:left\">\n<td style=\"width:13.7794%\">Level</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.3126%\">Prof Bonus</td>\n<td style=\"width:71.8517%\">Features</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:13.7794%\">1st</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.3126%\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"width:71.8517%\">@Compendium[gentleman-class.classfeatures.FNnu19d6dpbEthCf]{Fancy Dress}, @Compendium[gentleman-class.classfeatures.B6uljogi5fPLAwHM]{Social Ease}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:13.7794%\">2nd</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.3126%\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"width:71.8517%\">@Compendium[gentleman-class.classfeatures.BabnQGpEKTXLTM5y